Welcome to the Discord server for the speedrunning community of The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past!

The randomizer Discord for ALttP can be found here: https://discord.gg/BEPAD3Q

If you're looking to get started with the speedrun, here are some excellent resources:

* ALttP Speedrunning Wiki - https://alttp-wiki.net/index.php
* Tutorials + Resources - https://alttp-wiki.net/index.php/Tutorials_and_other_external_resources
* Practice Hack - http://milde.no/lttp
* Speedrun.com Leaderboard: http://www.speedrun.com/alttp

Helpasaur King is the resident bot which has many useful commands, listed here: https://github.com/greenham/alttp-bot/blob/master/README.md

There is a weekly Any% NMG No S+Q race every Sunday at 3:00 PM Eastern Time held on SpeedRunsLive. Everyone is welcome to join!

If you'd like to be pinged for various race categories, you can add yourself to the nmg-race and 100-race roles using the bot, like so:

`!role add nmg-race` or `!role add 100-race`